127
00:09:03,700 --> 00:09:04,180
Okay.

128
00:09:23,140 --> 00:09:23,820
Oh, Mo.

129
00:09:27,500 --> 00:09:29,620
You're always the lead guy.

130
00:09:30,260 --> 00:09:31,340
