146
00:10:22,180 --> 00:10:23,180
Are you insane?

147
00:10:24,140 --> 00:10:25,780
Do you know what you're doing?

148
00:10:26,980 --> 00:10:27,900
I'm helping you.

149
00:10:29,060 --> 00:10:30,420
