200
00:13:09,500 --> 00:13:11,260
Tomorrow, I'll tell Ms. Ling the truth!

201
00:13:11,620 --> 00:13:12,820
You won't be involved!

202
00:13:13,460 --> 00:13:14,100
Get lost!

203
00:13:46,380 --> 00:13:47,700
I heard

204
