243
00:16:24,700 --> 00:16:25,460
Hit them.

244
00:16:37,540 --> 00:16:38,300
Dazhuang!

245
00:16:39,100 --> 00:16:39,980
Loser.

246
00:17:43,420 --> 00:17:44,260
Hey, Miss.

247
00:17:46,100 --> 00:17:47,140
We're fighting.

248
00:17:48,820 --> 00:17:49,860
Stay away.

249
00:18:08,660 --> 00:18:10,100
