262
00:19:00,780 --> 00:19:02,300
Did Dazhuang tell you?

263
00:19:03,140 --> 00:19:04,420
Don't be silly.

264
00:19:05,860 --> 00:19:07,100
I brought you to the hospital

265
00:19:07,100 --> 00:19:09,100
