270
00:19:27,540 --> 00:19:28,940
Does my ID card say that?

271
00:19:28,940 --> 00:19:30,460
When you're in hospital,

272
00:19:30,460 --> 00:19:31,460
nobody but me

273
00:19:31,900 --> 00:19:33,020
has visited you.

274
00:19:37,620 --> 00:19:38,580
People usually get

275
00:19:39,100 --> 00:19:40,380
