279
00:19:47,020 --> 00:19:48,060
You can be a good model.

280
00:19:49,060 --> 00:19:50,780
If you're interested, give it a try.

281
00:19:51,140 --> 00:19:51,980
Model?

282
00:19:53,180 --> 00:19:54,620
